# Long-term Memory

This file stores important information that should persist across sessions.
The assistant reads this file at startup and updates it when new information should be remembered.

---

## User Information

- **Name**: (your name)
- **Role**: (your role or relationship with the assistant)
- **Status**: (e.g., "Often works on weekends", "Based in UTC+8")

## Preferences

*(Preferences learned over time — the assistant will fill these in automatically)*

## Project Context

- **Work Directory**: (set via `tools.workDir` in config.json — injected automatically as `{WORK_DIR}`)

## Important Notes

*(Things to remember across sessions — the assistant will update this automatically)*

---

*This file is automatically updated by nanobot when important information should be remembered.*
